M|gtag|tx|```javascript
M|gtag|tx|// Basic event
M|gtag|tx|gtag('event', 'signup_completed', {
M|gtag|'met|'em',
M|gtag|'pla|'free'
M|gtag|tx|});
M|gtag|tx|// Event w/ value
M|gtag|tx|gtag('event', 'purchase', {
M|gtag|'tra|'T12345',
M|gtag|'val|99.99,
M|gtag|'cur|'USD',
M|gtag|'ite|[{
M|gtag|'ite|'SKU123',
M|gtag|'ite|'pd Name',
M|gtag|'pri|99.99
M|gtag|tx|}]
M|gtag|tx|});
M|gtag|tx|// us properties
M|gtag|tx|gtag('set', 'user_properties', {
M|gtag|'use|'premium',
M|gtag|'pla|'pro'
M|gtag|tx|});
M|gtag|tx|// us ID (for logged-in us)
M|gtag|tx|gtag('config', 'GA_MEASUREMENT_ID', {
M|gtag|'use|'USER_ID'
M|gtag|tx|});
M|gtag|tx|```
