M|Crea|tx|1. **Collect the event** - Ensure event is firing in GA4
M|Crea|tx|2. **Mark as conversion** - Admin > Events > Mark as conversion
M|Crea|3. *|
M|Crea|it|Once per sn (leads, signups)
M|Crea|it|Every event (purchases)
M|Crea|tx|4. **Import to Google ad** - For conversion-optimized bidding
M|Conv|tx|```javascript
M|Conv|tx|// Event w/ conversion value
M|Conv|tx|gtag('event', 'purchase', {
M|Conv|'val|99.99,
M|Conv|'cur|'USD'
M|Conv|tx|});
M|Conv|tx|```
M|Conv|tx|Or set default value in GA4 Admin when marking conversion.
